Post Description:
This is a heartfelt tribute to teachers based on four real stories of parents who saw firsthand the creative lessons delivered by teachers during #HBL, and the care and enthusiasm put in to teach their children. It encapsulates the appreciation that many parents have for our teachers.

Once again, a very #HappyTeachersDay to all our educators. Enjoy the term break - you deserve it!

